title: The Durham Roast Session W DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & Chico Bean (Early Show)| Ep. 232
itunes:title: The Durham Roast Session W DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & Chico Bean (Early Show)| Ep. 232
description:
In the first of two sold out shows, superstar comedians DC Young fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean deliver another hilarious high energy comedy show. Chico Bean breaks down North Carolina culture and some of it's famous musical stars like Fantasia and Petey Pablo. Karlous Miller keeps the jokes coming and roasts the couple that's been together for 49 years and a beautiful fan from the audience also saves DC Young Fly's life with her lady parts. Plus coach Nolan Smith of Duke University stops thru to kick it with the crew behind the scenes. This is the coldest podcast!
